== TechDraw Workbench ==

=== Further TechDraw improvements ===

* The [[TechDraw_AreaDimension|Area dimension]] tool now properly accounts for holes in faces. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17740 Pull request #17740]
* Shape validation is now available and can be enabled in [[TechDraw_Preferences#Advanced|Preferences]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/18282 Pull request #18282]

